<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Radhika Tekade - Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #d9a7c7, #fffcdc);
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: purple;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 60%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        footer {
            background: purple;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: purple;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Hello, I'm Radhika 👋</h1>
    <p>Third Year Student | Machine Learning Enthusiast</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <p>
            I am a passionate Computer Science student.
            I love working on Machine Learning and Web Development projects.
        </p>
    </div>

    <h2>My Projects</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Fraud Detection using Machine Learning</h3>
        <p>Built a fraud detection model using ML algorithms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Smart Attendance System</h3>
        <p>Face recognition based attendance system using Python & OpenCV.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <p>Email: tekaderadhika4@gmail.com</p>
        <p>LinkedIn: <a href="#">Radhika Tekade</a></p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Radhika Tekade | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>